WEBVTT

03:00.224 --> 03:02.518
Absurd. You can't bring the dead
back to life.

03:02.602 --> 03:03.811
[Cho Hak-ju] It is the truth.

03:05.146 --> 03:06.147
And if it is?

03:07.106 --> 03:09.233
For what reason
would you show this plant to me?

03:09.859 --> 03:12.445
Are you suggesting
we resurrect our fallen soldiers
